# KAI Worlds

A collection of AI roleplay worlds built on the KAI Worlds architecture. Each world runs as a Claude Project — no coding required.

---

## Worlds

**[Late Night Radio](late_night_radio/README)** — A world about the 2am room. Two rooms, one radio, three people who cannot quite reach each other.

